lyrics.text:
Come as a child, come to the waters;
to the family of God, come, sons and daughters.
<br>Come to the river, the Lord, the Life-giver;
wash in the love that is sent from above.

Come, be baptized in the name of the Father;
come, be baptized in the name of the Son;
<br>come, be baptized in the name of the Spirit;
come, be baptized in love.

Come, be baptized in the name of the Father;
come, be baptized in the name of the Son;
<br>come, be baptized in the name of the Spirit;
come, be baptized in love.
